          "date": "2014-04-11 16:21:00.000000000",
          "tz": 540
        },
        "subject": "LU-4557 ext4: recalc percpu counters after journal",
        "message": "LU-4557 ext4: recalc percpu counters after journal\n\nthe percpu counters is initialized before replaying the journal,\nbut after the journal it should be recalculate to deal with the\npossibility of the percpu counters getting updated by the journal\nreplay.\n\nthe issue has been fixed in the new kernels (RHEL6 2.6.32-431.5.1,\nSLES11SP3 3.0.101-0.15), then it is not needed for these kernels.\n\nLustre-commit: ecaaa1bd05ab13feb4794f4f4c1f6bc64da7e8ad\nLustre-change: http://review.whamcloud.com/9908\n\nSigned-off-by: Hongchao Zhang <hongchao.zhang@intel.com>\nSigned-off-by: Shuichi Ihara <sihara@ddn.com>\nChange-Id: I2215efd74af3ba569ec08ae5b0454ca9f4a49673\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/b2_5"
    }
  },
